title: Bookmarks
content: It's no big deal but my music folder which is all YouTube wont sort by name all other bookmark folders I have sort fine. When I sort by name it is all random. This issue started about 2 or 3 Firefox updates ago before it would sort by name no problem I am using 118.0.1 I don't know if YouTube has changed something with there icons or its just a bug in Fire Fox
